cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with document retrieval, which is a core topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). It also involves data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms for efficient search (cs.CC). The use of relevance measures and the consideration of dynamic scenarios suggest a connection to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
